\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 axis and the spectrometer field.
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Sanders94"
literal "true"

\end_inset

 The factor of 10
\begin_inset Formula $^{5}$
\end_inset

